      <li><strong>API Specifications:</strong> How to activate and control shields programmatically</li>
      <li><strong>Protocol Definitions:</strong> Communication protocols for secure wireless interactions</li>
      <li><strong>Integration Guidelines:</strong> How to integrate shields into existing systems</li>
      <li><strong>Security Measures:</strong> Specific defenses against known attack vectors</li>
      <li><strong>Implementation Examples:</strong> Reference code in multiple languages</li>
      <li><strong>Certification Process:</strong> How to achieve WIA-AIR-SHIELD compliance</li>
    </ul>

